ygData.msgSnippet: Could be.  I killed Tranix once and all I got were these lousy Rusty Spiked Shoulderpads.  When I killed him, I was fresh from selling a bunch of stuff and
ygData.messageBody:
Could be. I killed Tranix once and all I got were these lousy Rusty Spiked
Shoulderpads. When I killed him, I was fresh from selling a bunch of stuff
and still had a crude stein and no weapon. It was pretty fun killing him
with all the level 8-10 newbies cheering me on though =)

> -----Original Message-----
> From: Whitcraft,David [SMTP:DWHITCRAFT@...]
> Sent: Monday, August 30, 1999 4:06 PM
> To: 'EQCheats@onelist.com'
> Subject: [EQCheats] Crown of King Tranix
>
> From: "Whitcraft,David" <DWHITCRAFT@...>
>
> Crown of King Tranix? Anyone know how to obtain this item? King Tranix is
> the head gnoll in BB, isn't he? I have heard him once before last night,
> hollering back when I played a young warrior. I was on my way through BB
> last night with my shaman when I heard Tranix hollering, I stopped, and he
> hit me frm behind. Quick fight, but he didn't have anything but a bronze
> mace (was green to this 28th shaman). Any clues? Suppose it could have
> something to do with the named gnolls out in EK?
